{
  "design_notes": "Easy chart designed to follow the energy curve smoothly. Stick strictly to quarter and half notes to handle the 184 BPM tempo comfortably. Intro uses half notes on even beats; build increases the density slightly using 2-beat step patterns. The main drops use a comfortable Tap-Tap-Tap-Rest quarter note pattern (NPS under 2.5) with sequential, well-timed holds. All holds strictly correspond to analyzed sustain candidates within the 10-20% share budget. No crossovers or footswitches are present to respect the easy difficulty budget.",
